  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>A varied buffet breakfast is served in the dining room on the first floor or out on the terrace when the weather's good.</p>
<p>Hotel Lenno's restaurant  produces some fantastic food! They're inspired by regional and international cuisine and everything tastes fresh. Why not try it out one evening, they have an a la carte menu which is payable locally. There's also a small bar for a night-cap or pre-dinner drink.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
