  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>This is the perfect hotel to get away from it all. Lenno is a small town with just a handful of cafés and a beautiful tree-lined promenade. The hotel's right on the lake, about 100 metres from the ferry port, so you can find a spot with a nice view and settle down with a good book. The food here is one of the reasons we keep going back - the a la carte dinners are wonderful and you get to enjoy lake views as you dine. </p>]]></listingDescription>
