  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Double Attic Rooms</strong> are on the top floor of the hotel and have a sloped roof. They're spacious and the glass skylights mean they're lovely and bright. These rooms have a double bed and sleep up to four people. Facilities include air-conditioning, TV, safe, minibar, hairdryer and a bath or shower.  </p>
<p><strong>Twin Attic Rooms</strong> are also located on the top floor and have a sloped roof. These rooms have twin beds and sleep up to three people. The bathroom has a bath or a shower (please request if you have a preference).  </p>
<p><strong>Side Lake View Rooms</strong> have partial views of the lake from the window and sleep up to three people.</p>
<p><strong>Lake View Rooms </strong>sleep two people. You can request to upgrade to a Lake view room with a balcony for a supplement (balcony rooms cannot be guaranteed).*</p>
<p><strong>Apartments</strong> sleep up to four people and have a balcony with pool views. The extra bed is a double sofa bed. They're located in the annex. </p>
<p><em>*Please note that some of the lake view rooms are partially blocked by trees. </em></p>]]></roomsDescription>
